        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-600 mb-10 italic border-l-4 border-medicalTeal pl-6">
          "Why does hair turn white?" Yeh sawaal har ofsi ke mann mein aata hai — chahe aap 20 saal ke hon and mirror mein pehli white hair dikhi ho, ya 30s mein hain and achanak greying badh gayi ho. Aaj hum complete science ke saath samjhayenge of hair white kyun happen, premature greying ke actual causes what/can hain, and what/can isfrom rokna ya reverfrom karna possible hai.
        </p>

        <p>India mein premature greying ek bahut common concern hai. Studies ke according Indian population mein 20-30 age group ke approximately 30-40% log premature greying experience karte hain — jo global average from zyada hai. Lekin iska matlab yeh nahi of yeh normal hai. Iske peeche definite scientific reasons hain jo samajhna zaroori hai. Aur haan, kuch cases mein sahi treatment from <a href="can-white-hair-turn-black-again.php">white hair ko wapas black karna</a> also possible hai.</p>

        

<p>Especially for the <strong>Indian climate and lifestyle</strong>, maintaining healthy hair and skin requires specialized care that addresses local environmental factors, diet, and genetics.</p>

<h2>The Science of Hair Color — Baalon Ka Rang Kaifrom Aata Hai?</h2>

        <p>Pehle yeh samajhte hain of baalon ko rang kaifrom milta hai. Aapke har ek hair follicle mein special cells happen jinhe <strong>melanocytes</strong> kehte hain. Yeh melanocytes ek pigment produce karte hain jiska naam hai <strong>melanin</strong>. Yeh melanin hi hai jo aapke baalon ko, skin ko, and aankhon ko color deta hai.</p>

        <p>Melanin do types ka hota hai:</p>

        <p><strong>Eumelanin:</strong> Yeh dark pigment hai. Agar aapke follicles zyada eumelanin produce karte hain, toh aapke hair black ya dark brown honge. Indian population mein mostly eumelanin dominant hota hai — isliye humari majority ke hair kaale happen.</p>

        <p><strong>Pheomelanin:</strong> Yeh lighter, reddish-yellow pigment hai. Jab pheomelanin zyada hota hai toh hair blonde, red, ya light brown happen. European populations mein yeh zyada common hai.</p>

        <p>Jab melanocytes melanin banana band kar dete hain ya reduce kar dete hain — tab hair apna color kho dete hain and white/grey dikhte hain. Grey hair actually ek mix hai — kuch melanin ban raha hai, kuch nahi. <strong>Completely white hair matlab melanin production zero hai us follicle mein.</strong></p>

        
