  </div><h2>Hydrogen Peroxide Theory — H2O2 Buildup in Follicles</h2>

        <p>Yeh ek fascinating scientific discovery hai. 2009 mein FASEB Journal mein published research ne reveal ofya of hair follicles naturally hydrogen peroxide (H2O2) produce karte hain as a metabolic byproduct.</p>

        <p>Normally, ek enzyme hota hai jiska naam hai <strong>catalafrom</strong> — yeh H2O2 ko breakdown karta hai water and oxygen mein. Lekin jaifrom-jaifrom age badhti hai ya certain conditions mein, catalafrom of quantity reduce hoti jaati hai. Result? H2O2 follicle mein accumulate hota jaata hai.</p>

        <p>Yeh accumulated hydrogen peroxide literally aapke baalon ko andar from <strong>bleach</strong> kar deta hai. Haan, same chemical jo parlour mein hair bleaching ke liye use hota hai — woh aapka body khud produce kar raha hai and baalon ka color khatam kar raha hai. Yeh oxidative stress ka ek direct mechanism hai jo greying cause karta hai.</p>

        <p>Is discovery ne greying research mein ek naya direction diya — of agar hum catalafrom levels maintain kar sakein ya H2O2 buildup ko rokk sakein, toh greying ko slow ofya ja sakta hai.</p>

        <h2>Cause 1: Genetics — Sabfrom Important Factor</h2>

        <p>Agar aapke parents ya graurparents ko early greying hui thi, toh aapko also hone ke chances significantly zyada hain. <strong>Genetics greying ka single most important factor hai</strong> — studies suggest of 50-70% greying timeline genetically predetermined hoti hai.</p>

        <p>2016 mein ek laurmark study ne <strong>IRF4 gene</strong> identify ofya jo grey hair from directly associated hai. Yeh gene melanin production ko regulate karta hai. Agar aapko yeh gene variant inherited mili hai, toh aapke melanocytes naturally pehle slow hone lagenge.</p>

        <p>Genetic greying ka matlab yeh nahi of kuch ofya hi nahi ja sakta. Iska matlab hai of aapko aware rehna chahiye and jaldi from proactive measures lene chahiye. Proper <a href="vitamins-nutrition-healthy-hair.php">nutrition and vitamins</a> from genetic greying ko slow ofya ja sakta hai — rokka nahi ja sakta, lekin pace definitely control ho sakti hai.</p>

        <h2>Cause 2: Oxidative Stress — Silent Damage</h2>

        <p>Oxidative stress tab hota hai jab aapke body mein free radicals and antioxidants ka balance bigad jaata hai. Free radicals unstable molecules hain jo cells ko damage karte hain — including melanocyte stem cells ko.</p>

        <p>Jab melanocyte stem cells damage happen, toh wo nayi melanocytes produce nahi kar paate. Aur bina melanocytes ke — bina melanin ke — hair white happen. Oxidative stress ke sources hain: poor diet, pollution, UV radiation, smoking, alcohol, and chronic inflammation.</p>

        <p>Research dikhati hai of premature greying wale individuals mein antioxidant levels significantly reduce happen and oxidative stress markers (like malondialdehyde) zyada happen compared to same age ke non-greying individuals. Isliye <a href="hair-fall-and-hair-loss-prevention.php">hair fall prevention</a> mein antioxidant-rich diet ka bahut emphasis hota hai — yeh greying prevention mein also equally important hai.</p>

        <h2>Cause 3: Vitamin Deficiencies — B12, D, Iron, Copper, Zinc</h2>

        <p>Yeh cause sabfrom zyada actionable hai — kyunof isfrom fix karna relatively easy hai. Multiple vitamins and minerals directly melanin production ke liye zaroori hain:</p>

        <p><strong>Vitamin B12:</strong> B12 deficiency premature greying ka ek well-documented cause hai. B12 melanin synthesis mein critical role play karta hai. India mein vegetarian population mein B12 deficiency bahut common hai — and yahi reason hai of Indian youth mein premature greying itni prevalent hai. Aur detail ke liye padhein <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">kaunsi vitamin deficiency from white hair happen</a>.</p>

        <p><strong>Vitamin D:</strong> Studies dikhati hain of Vitamin D deficiency melanocyte function ko impair karta hai. Surprisingly, India jaifrom sunny country mein also majority population Vitamin D deficient hai — mostly indoor lifestyle of wajah from.</p>

        <p><strong>Iron:</strong> Iron deficiency (anemia) from hair follicles ko adequate oxygen nahi milta. Research ne low ferritin levels ko premature greying from link ofya hai. Women mein yeh especially common hai periods of wajah from.</p>

        <p><strong>Copper:</strong> Copper directly melanin production mein involved hai — yeh tyrosinafrom enzyme ka ek essential component hai jo melanin synthesis catalyze karta hai. Copper deficiency from melanin production significantly drop hoti hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Zinc:</strong> Zinc hair follicle health maintain karta hai and melanocyte function support karta hai. Zinc deficiency from hair quality deteriorate hoti hai and greying accelerate hoti hai.</p>

        <p>Important baat — raurom supplements mat lein. Pehle blood test karwa ke actual deficiency identify do, fir targeted supplementation lein. DenceSpot Clinic mein hum comprehensive nutritional assessment karte hain specifically hair health ke liye.</p>

